{"tid":1004370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 警察學院爆食物中毒　25男食咖哩薯仔炆排骨拼魚腐飯後腹瀉","createTime":"2019-02-01T11:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T16:25:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":189,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"951f943f9faef0a97d5fdb94a4d73561c1fad574","tid":1004370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心今（1日）公布香港警察學院懷疑食物中毒個案，當中25男，年齡介乎19至41歲。他們在1月29日在學院內用午膳後，約8至23小時後出現腹痛和腹瀉等病徵，而他們均曾於學堂內曾食咖哩薯仔炆排骨拼魚腐飯，2人曾經求醫，無需入院，所有人情況穩定。<br />\n食環署回覆指，已派員到有關處所調查，該處所衞生情況尚可。食環署人員在該處所已抽取環境樣本及食物樣本作化驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/290787/警察學院爆食物中毒-25男食咖哩薯仔炆排骨拼魚腐飯後腹瀉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F290787%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E7%88%86%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92-25%E7%94%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%92%96%E5%93%A9%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E7%82%86%E6%8E%92%E9%AA%A8%E6%8B%BC%E9%AD%9A%E8%85%90%E9%A3%AF%E5%BE%8C%E8%85%B9%E7%80%89&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=cc0ec49b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/290787/警察學院爆食物中毒-25男食咖哩薯仔炆排骨拼魚腐飯後腹瀉</a>"},{"pid":"d87c069211acc1ce5e732471abaa5888521078ad","tid":1004370,"uid":117276,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60e4ca5d039daf3c15623f99c0ad0739cdf4a11","tid":1004370,"uid":11301,"like":290,"dislike":0,"score":290,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"阿sir中毒唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15764afb249ddd2c6934e9d97216b160d8b1f22e","tid":1004370,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d60e4ca5d039daf3c15623f99c0ad0739cdf4a11","tid":1004370,"uid":11301,"like":290,"dislike":0,"score":290